satellite.heading: Satellite
satellite.specs:
Akụkụ: 50x58x64 mm
1P PocketQube
Arọ: 245 gr
Akụrụngwa: aluminum, gold, fiberglass, na electronic components.
Orbit: Elu 525 ± 25 km; ọchịchọ: SSO 97.6 ± 0.1°
Ihe mmalite: PSLV (Ụgbọ Mwepụta Satellite Polar) nke ISRO na-arụ

antenna.heading: Antenna/ihe ọkpụkpụ
antenna.specs:
Akụkụ: 6m (dayameta) na 1.2m (ịdị elu)
Arọ: 46kg
Akụrụngwa: aluminom, osisi epoxy mirrored, dome aluminom ọla edo kwụsịtụrụ site na nhazi ihe nrụnye.
